you'd share a meal with me.

00:18:13.510 --> 00:18:16.554 position:50% align:center
You gave me your word
that you would!

00:18:16.638 --> 00:18:22.811 position:50% align:center
Licht, please! Please don't go!
I'm begging you to come back!

00:18:22.894 --> 00:18:26.147 position:50% align:center
You're just a liar!

00:18:38.743 --> 00:18:40.995 position:50% align:center
[HINA]
I hate you.

00:19:02.308 --> 00:19:03.476 position:50% align:center
[NICOLA]
I see.

00:19:03.560 --> 00:19:05.603 position:50% align:center
[HINA gasps]

00:19:05.687 --> 00:19:07.147 position:50% align:center
You have it.

00:19:07.230 --> 00:19:10.191 position:50% align:center
That man never even took
that ballot away from you.

00:19:10.275 --> 00:19:12.736 position:50% align:center
[gasps]
You're one of them!

00:19:14.988 --> 00:19:15.989 position:50% align:center
[NICOLA]
Hm!

00:19:16.072 --> 00:19:19.909 position:50% align:center
