to get the wrong idea.

00:19:23.997 --> 00:19:25.665 position:50% align:center
I don't care about that thing.

00:19:25.749 --> 00:19:28.543 position:50% align:center
I have no interest in
the ballot whatsoever.

00:19:28.626 --> 00:19:31.671 position:50% align:center
In fact, my goal was
to come and thank you.

00:19:31.755 --> 00:19:33.298 position:50% align:center
Glad you're here.

00:19:33.381 --> 00:19:35.550 position:50% align:center
To... thank me?

00:19:35.633 --> 00:19:38.845 position:50% align:center
Yes. Thank you, ma'am.

00:19:38.928 --> 00:19:44.017 position:50% align:center
With your help today, we were
able to locate the Ace at last.

00:19:44.100 --> 00:19:45.518 position:50% align:center
