to file a positive report.

00:19:50.357 --> 00:19:52.901 position:50% align:center
One for my real
commanding officer.

00:19:52.984 --> 00:19:55.403 position:50% align:center
What do you mean "real" one?

00:19:55.487 --> 00:19:56.988 position:50% align:center
