I gotta say,

00:19:57.072 --> 00:19:59.783 position:50% align:center
that was unbelievably
cool earlier.

00:19:59.866 --> 00:20:03.161 position:50% align:center
He was able to blow our men
away just by walking.

00:20:03.244 --> 00:20:05.705 position:50% align:center
He must've been moving faster
than the speed of sound

00:20:05.789 --> 00:20:06.873 position:50% align:center
or something.

00:20:06.956 --> 00:20:08.500 position:50% align:center
And that big finishing move?

00:20:08.583 --> 00:20:11.002 position:50% align:center
Oh man, he went up in the
sky and was like, boom.

00:20:11.086 --> 00:20:13.755 position:50% align:center
Honestly it was more like a
bombing run than a fight!

00:20:13.838 --> 00:20:15.632 position:50% align:center
