shockwave would've gotten him.

00:20:21.596 --> 00:20:24.683 position:50% align:center
How do you even
beat that? Oh yeah!

00:20:31.272 --> 00:20:36.152 position:50% align:center
[NICOLA]
Yes, it's me. Yeah. Yep.

00:20:36.236 --> 00:20:38.363 position:50% align:center
