What is going on here?

00:20:41.783 --> 00:20:44.577 position:50% align:center
Yeah. I'm absolutely positive.

00:20:44.661 --> 00:20:48.123 position:50% align:center
Heh. I know because I
saw everything myself.

00:20:48.206 --> 00:20:54.045 position:50% align:center
Identification code oh-oh-one,
the Ace of Flashing Strikes.

00:20:54.129 --> 00:20:59.426 position:50% align:center
Licht Bach. He's still alive.

